    GraphRewriting.GL.Menu
    GraphRewriting.GL.Canvas
    GraphRewriting.GL.HyperEdge
  Extensions:
    UnicodeSyntax
    FlexibleInstances
    FlexibleContexts
    MultiParamTypeClasses
    TypeSynonymInstances
  GHC-Options:    -fno-warn-duplicate-exports
